    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Falsifiable Predictions</h2>
      <p class="themed-text-secondary mb-4">Six structural predictions from the derivation. Each is testable. Each would weaken or falsify the framework if it fails.</p>

      <div class="themed-surface border rounded-lg p-6 overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-left">
          <thead>
            <tr class="themed-border border-b">
              <th class="pb-3 themed-text-muted">#</th>
